#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod.json
msgid "folding and adjustable stock"
msgid_plural "folding and adjustable stocks"
msgstr[0] "摺疊可調式槍托"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod.json
msgid ""
"This mod improves recoil and accuracy but needs unfolding before use.  It "
"increases the time needed to wield the weapon."
msgstr "此改裝件能改善後坐力和精準度，但使用前需展開。它會增加舉槍所需的時間。"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod.json
msgid "stock"
msgstr "槍托"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod.json
msgid "lightweight bipod"
msgid_plural "lightweight bipods"
msgstr[0] "輕量化兩腳架"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift metal bipod looped around the barrel and used to provide a "
"forward rest to reduce motion.  Aside from a very slight increase in weight "
"there are no drawbacks."
msgstr "一個臨時製作的金屬兩腳架，環繞槍管，用於提供前置支撐以減少晃動。除了輕微增加重量外，沒有其他缺點。"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod.json
msgid "underbarrel"
msgstr "下掛式"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod.json
msgid "neck strap"
msgid_plural "neck straps"
msgstr[0] "頸帶"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod.json
msgid ""
"A neck strap allows a pistol to be worn like a piece of clothing.  It offers"
" no protection, but improves accuracy when held taught."
msgstr "頸帶允許手槍像衣物一樣佩戴。它不提供防護，但在拉緊時能提高精準度。"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod.json
msgid "sling"
msgstr "槍帶"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod.json
msgid "peep sight"
msgid_plural "peep sights"
msgstr[0] "覘孔式瞄具"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod.json
msgid ""
"A rear sight aperture that can adjust for windage and elevation allowing for"
" very accurate aiming through a small, framed circle. Also known as a "
"diopter sight."
msgstr "一種可調節風偏和高低的後瞄具孔徑，通過一個帶框的小圓孔實現非常精準的瞄準。也稱為屈光瞄具。"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod.json
msgid "sights"
msgstr "瞄準具"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod.json
msgid "SUSAT scope"
msgid_plural "SUSAT scopes"
msgstr[0] "SUSAT 瞄準鏡"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod.json
msgid ""
