#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod_obsolete.json
msgid "auto-fire rifle assembly"
msgid_plural "auto-fire rifle assemblys"
msgstr[0] "全自動步槍組件"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod_obsolete.json
msgid ""
"Fabricated parts necessary to convert a valid semi-automatic rifle to a "
"selective fire weapon with a burst size of 15 rounds.  However it reduces "
"accuracy while increasing recoil."
msgstr "將適用的半自動步槍改裝為15發點射可選射擊武器的必要自制零件。但會降低精度並增加後坐力。"

