msgstr[0] "可選全自動組件"

#: .\modern_extras\modern_mod_obsolete.json
msgid ""
"A fabricated cam and sear, combined with an auto-fire rifle assembly, used "
"to convert a valid semi-automatic rifle to a selective fire weapon with a "
"burst sizes of 3 and 10 rounds.  However it reduces accuracy while "
"increasing recoil."
msgstr "一個自制的凸輪和阻鐵，結合全自動步槍組件，用於將適用的半自動步槍改裝為可選射擊武器，支持3發和10發點射。但會降低精度並增加後坐力。"

