#: .\modern_extras\overrides_gun.json
msgid ""
"A uniquely designed pistol caliber carbine with an integral folding stock "
"and that makes use of a large variety of 9mm magazines."
msgstr "一款獨特設計的手槍口徑卡賓槍，配有內置摺疊槍托，可使用多種9毫米彈匣。"

#: .\modern_extras\overrides_gun.json
